Products.RichDescription:
CONTINENTAL NATURALLY TASTY RECIPE BASE BEEF STEW 63 GR

Continental Naturally Tasty Beef Stew is a recipe mix full of natural ingredients, so you can create a delicious meal the whole family will enjoy. Just add... 1 tablespoon sunflower oil 500g chuck or blade steak, trimmed and cubed 2 cups (150g) sliced mushrooms 1 pack Recipe Base 1 cups (375mL) water Pasta to serve Preparation time: 10 minutes Cooking time: 1 hours Simply... 1. Heat oil in a large saucepan and brown beef and mushrooms. 2. Add Recipe Base and water, bring to the boil stirring. 3. Cover and cook over a low heat for 1-1 hours until meat is tender. Serve with pasta and steamed broccoli. For more recipes, see www.continental.com.au/recipe-ideas.html. At Continental, we love food the way you do. We know how much you value good, nutritious, flavourful food, as well as authentic home cooking. It feels good to cook, and even better to bring pleasure to the ones you love, through the food you put on the table. For over 50 years now, our chefs at Continental have combined their expertise, love of flavour, and only the finest ingredients to help you create great tasting meals every day. Our chefs work closely with Continental farmers to make sure their love for growing great food makes a real difference in Continental products and in the meals you cook with them.Go to http://continental.com.au/ to find more recipe inspirations and additional flavours such as sheperds pie, curried sausages, spaghetti Bolognese, beef stroganoff, chicken curry, beef stew, chicken risotto, swedish meatballs, chicken korma and many more instant sauces.

4 star health star rating

Recipe base includes flavour notes of paprika, rosemary and thyme

Just 10 minutes preparation time

Full of natural ingredients

Recipe base comes in a convenient single use sachet
